Package: rdrsimulate
Title: Simulate Microbial Communities and their rRNA:rDNA Ratios
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("David", "Wilkins", email = "david@wilkox.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 'rdrsimulate' simulates microbial communities with a mixture of metabolic states and ribosomal amplification levels, and computes rRNA:rDNA ratios.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
